{"schemaVersion":2,"book":"3JN","chapters":{"1":{"1":{"text":"El anciano al muy amado Gayo, a quien yo amo en la verdad.","segments":[{"text":"El","strong":"G3588","morph":"DNSM"},{"text":"anciano","strong":"G4245","morph":"JNSM"},{"text":"al"},{"text":"muy"},{"text":"amado"},{"text":"Gayo,","strong":"G1050","morph":"NDSM"},{"text":"a"},{"text":"quien"},{"text":"yo"},{"text":"amo","strong":"G25","morph":"RP1NS"},{"text":"en","strong":"G1722","morph":"P"},{"text":"la"},{"text":"verdad.","strong":"G225","morph":"NDSF"}],"strongs":["G1050","G1722","G225","G25","G3588","G4245"]},"2":{"text":"Amado, mi oración es que tú seas prosperado en todas las cosas, y que tengas salud, así como prospera tu alma.","segments":[{"text":"Amado,","strong":"G27","morph":"JVSM"},{"text":"mi"},{"text":"oración"},{"text":"es"},{"text":"que"},{"text":"tú","strong":"G4571","morph":"RP2AS"},{"text":"seas"},{"text":"prosperado","strong":"G2137","morph":"VPPN"},{"text":"en","strong":"G4012","morph":"P"},{"text":"todas"},{"text":"las"},{"text":"cosas,","strong":"G3956","morph":"JGPN"},{"text":"y","strong":"G2532","morph":"C"},{"text":"que"},{"text":"tengas"},{"text":"salud,","strong":"G5198","morph":"VPAN"},{"text":"así"},{"text":"como","strong":"G2531","morph":"B"},{"text":"prospera","strong":"G2137","morph":"VPPI3S"},{"text":"tu","strong":"G4675","morph":"RP2GS"},{"text":"alma.","strong":"G5590","morph":"DNSF"}],"strongs":["G2137","G2531","G2532","G27","G3956","G4012","G4571","G4675","G5198","G5590"]},"3":{"text":"Pues mucho me regocijé cuando vinieron los hermanos y dieron testimonio de tu verdad, y de cómo tú andas en la verdad.","segments":[{"text":"Pues","strong":"G1063","morph":"C"},{"text":"mucho","strong":"G3029","morph":"B"},{"text":"me"},{"text":"regocijé","strong":"G5463","morph":"VAPI1S"},{"text":"cuando"},{"text":"vinieron","strong":"G2064","morph":"VPUP-PGM"},{"text":"los"},{"text":"hermanos","strong":"G80","morph":"NGPM"},{"text":"y","strong":"G2532","morph":"C"},{"text":"dieron"},{"text":"testimonio","strong":"G3140","morph":"VPAP-PGM"},{"text":"de"},{"text":"tu","strong":"G4675","morph":"RP2GS"},{"text":"verdad,","strong":"G225","morph":"DDSF"},{"text":"y"},{"text":"de"},{"text":"cómo","strong":"G2531","morph":"B"},{"text":"tú"},{"text":"andas","strong":"G4043","morph":"RP2NS"},{"text":"en","strong":"G1722","morph":"P"},{"text":"la"},{"text":"verdad.","strong":"G225","morph":"NDSF"}],"strongs":["G1063","G1722","G2064","G225","G2531","G2532","G3029","G3140","G4043","G4675","G5463","G80"]},"4":{"text":"No tengo mayor gozo que el oír que mis hijos andan en la verdad.","segments":[{"text":"No","strong":"G3756","morph":"T"},{"text":"tengo","strong":"G2192","morph":"VPAI1S"},{"text":"mayor","strong":"G3186","morph":"JASF"},{"text":"gozo","strong":"G5479","morph":"NASF"},{"text":"que"},{"text":"el","strong":"G2443","morph":"C"},{"text":"oír","strong":"G191","morph":"VPAS1S"},{"text":"que"},{"text":"mis","strong":"G1699","morph":"RS1APN"},{"text":"hijos","strong":"G5043","morph":"DAPN"},{"text":"andan","strong":"G4043","morph":"VPAP-SAM"},{"text":"en","strong":"G1722","morph":"P"},{"text":"la"},{"text":"verdad.","strong":"G225","morph":"NDSF"}],"strongs":["G1699","G1722","G191","G2192","G225","G2443","G3186","G3756","G4043","G5043","G5479"]},"5":{"text":"Amado, fielmente haces todo lo que haces para con los hermanos, y con los extranjeros,","segments":[{"text":"Amado,","strong":"G27","morph":"JVSM"},{"text":"fielmente","strong":"G4103","morph":"JASN"},{"text":"haces"},{"text":"todo"},{"text":"lo"},{"text":"que"},{"text":"haces"},{"text":"para"},{"text":"con"},{"text":"los","strong":"G3588","morph":"DAPM"},{"text":"hermanos,","strong":"G80","morph":"NAPM"},{"text":"y"},{"text":"con"},{"text":"los","strong":"G3588","morph":"DAPM"},{"text":"extranjeros,"}],"strongs":["G27","G3588","G4103","G80"]},"6":{"text":"los cuales han dado testimonio de tu amor en presencia de la iglesia; a los cuales si encaminares en su jornada como es digno según Dios, harás