iótrefes, que ama tener la preeminencia entre ellos, no nos recibe.","segments":[{"text":"Yo"},{"text":"he"},{"text":"escrito","strong":"G1125","morph":"VAAI1S"},{"text":"a"},{"text":"la","strong":"G3588","morph":"DDSF"},{"text":"iglesia;","strong":"G1577","morph":"NDSF"},{"text":"mas"},{"text":"Diótrefes,","strong":"G1361","morph":"NNSM"},{"text":"que"},{"text":"ama"},{"text":"tener"},{"text":"la"},{"text":"preeminencia"},{"text":"entre"},{"text":"ellos,","strong":"G846","morph":"RP-GPF"},{"text":"no","strong":"G3756","morph":"T"},{"text":"nos","strong":"G2248","morph":"RP1AP"},{"text":"recibe.","strong":"G1926","morph":"VPUI3S"}],"strongs":["G1125","G1361","G1577","G1926","G2248","G3588","G3756","G846"]},"10":{"text":"Por esta causa, si yo viniere, recordaré las obras que hace parloteando con palabras maliciosas contra nosotros; y no contento con estas cosas, no recibe a los hermanos, y a los que quieren recibirlos se los impide, y los expulsa de la iglesia.","segments":[{"text":"Por","strong":"G1223","morph":"P"},{"text":"esta"},{"text":"causa,","strong":"G5124","morph":"RD-ASN"},{"text":"si","strong":"G1437","morph":"C"},{"text":"yo"},{"text":"viniere,"},{"text":"recordaré","strong":"G5279","morph":"VFAI1S"},{"text":"las","strong":"G3588","morph":"DAPN"},{"text":"obras","strong":"G2041","morph":"NAPN"},{"text":"que","strong":"G3739","morph":"RR-APN"},{"text":"hace","strong":"G4160","morph":"VPAI3S"},{"text":"parloteando","strong":"G5396","morph":"VPAP-SNM"},{"text":"con"},{"text":"palabras","strong":"G3056","morph":"NDPM"},{"text":"maliciosas"},{"text":"contra"},{"text":"nosotros;","strong":"G2248","morph":"RP1AP"},{"text":"y","strong":"G2532","morph":"C"},{"text":"no","strong":"G3361","morph":"T"},{"text":"contento","strong":"G714","morph":"VPPP-SNM"},{"text":"con","strong":"G1909","morph":"P"},{"text":"estas"},{"text":"cosas,","strong":"G5125","morph":"RD-DPM"},{"text":"no","strong":"G3777","morph":"C"},{"text":"recibe","strong":"G1926","morph":"RP-NSM"},{"tex